'''2021年蘇伊士運河阻塞事件'''（{{lang-en|2021 Suez Canal obstruction}}）發生在2021年3月23日[[埃及標準時間|埃及標準時間]]上午7时40分，400米長的[[長榮海運|長榮海運]][[貨櫃船|貨櫃船]][[長賜輪|長賜輪]]在[[埃及|埃及]][[蘇伊士運河|蘇伊士運河]][[擱淺|擱淺]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |first1=Magdy |last1=Samaan |first2=Shawn |last2=Deng |first3=Sarah |last3=El Sirgany |first4=Mostafa |last4=Salem |first5=Lauren |last5=Said-Moorhouse |title=Suez Canal blocked by traffic jam after massive container ship runs aground |url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/24/middleeast/suez-canal-container-ship-intl-hnk/index.html |access-date=2021-03-25 |website=CNN |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324235023/https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/24/middleeast/suez-canal-container-ship-intl-hnk/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這艘船在[[沙塵暴|沙塵暴]]中受風速高達40節（每小時74公里）的強風吹襲而偏離航道<ref>{{Cite news |last=Higham |first=Aliss |date=2021-03-25 |title=Suez Canal live map: Ever Given still grounded as rescuers claim 'it might take weeks' |work=Daily Express |url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/1414802/Suez-canal-live-map-Suez-Canal-blocked-ever-given-tracker-evg |access-date=2021-03-26 |archive-date=2021-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326000336/https://www.express.co.uk/news/world/1414802/Suez-canal-live-map-Suez-Canal-blocked-ever-given-tracker-evg |dead-url=no }}</ref>，继而與運河底部碰撞並擱淺，完全阻塞了運河<ref>{{Cite news |date=2021-03-25 |title=Container ship facts: Egypt's Suez Canal blocked by massive boat |work=BBC |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/newsround/56511717 |access-date=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2021-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326031201/https://www.bbc.co.uk/newsround/56511717 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。擱淺的河段恰屬未扩建區域，河道窄小，因此其他船隻無法繞行<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-03-24|title=Suez Canal Stays Blocked Despite Efforts to Free Stuck Ship|language=en|work=Bloomberg.com|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-24/suez-canal-blockage-closer-to-resolution-on-efforts-to-move-ship|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326235941/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=5436b0f0-8e8f-11eb-832b-0f82759c1da4&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMS0wMy0yNC9zdWV6LWNhbmFsLWJsb2NrYWdlLWNsb3Nlci10by1yZXNvbHV0aW9uLW9uLWVmZm9ydHMtdG8tbW92ZS1zaGlw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。造成超过300艘船隻排隊等候，其中至少有15艘船隻因此{{tsl|en|Anchorage (maritime)|下錨}}<ref>{{cite news |title=埃及方面已为搁浅货轮救援制定多套预案 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2021-03/28/c_1127263347.htm |agency=新华社 |date=2021-03-28 |accessdate=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328223527/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2021-03/28/c_1127263347.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="upi">{{Cite news |last=Uria |first=Daniel |date=2021-03-23 |title=Grounded container ship blocks traffic on Suez Canal |work=United Press International |url=https://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2021/03/23/Egypt-container-ship-blocks-Suez-Canal/4591616550164/ |access-date=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324185236/https://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2021/03/23/Egypt-container-ship-blocks-Suez-Canal/4591616550164/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Meade |first=Richard |date=2021-03-25 |title=Suez blockage extends as salvors fail to free Ever Given |work=Lloyd's List |url=https://lloydslist.maritimeintelligence.informa.com/LL1136246/Suez-blockage-extends-as-salvors-fail-to-free-Ever-Given |access-date=2021-03-26 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325215810/https://lloydslist.maritimeintelligence.informa.com/LL1136246/Suez-blockage-extends-as-salvors-fail-to-free-Ever-Given |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終長賜輪於六天後（29日）成功脫困，蘇伊士運河不久後亦重新恢復雙向航運<ref name="Pippa Stevens">{{Cite web |title=Suez Canal traffic resumes after cargo ship Ever Given is moving again |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/03/29/suez-canal-traffic-resumes-after-cargo-ship-ever-given-is-removed.html |access-date=2021-03-29 |date=2021-03-29 |author=Pippa Stevens |publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |archive-date=2021-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329141033/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/03/29/suez-canal-traffic-resumes-after-cargo-ship-ever-given-is-removed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Debre"/>。

== 背景 ==
[[File:EVER_GIVEN_(49643352087).jpg|thumb]]的長賜輪，攝於2020年3月|left]]
[[蘇伊士運河|蘇伊士運河]]於1869年正式通航，為世界上最重要的水上航路之一<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|last=Gambrell|first=Jon|date=2021-03-23|title=Massive cargo ship turns sideways, blocks Egypt's Suez Canal|work={{tsl|en|KARE (TV)||KARE (TV)}}|agency=Associated Press|url=https://www.kare11.com/article/news/nation-world/cargo-ship-suez-canal-trapped/507-3ca6964c-3ac2-4b13-867c-38d87366ea5d|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326031159/https://www.kare11.com/article/news/nation-world/cargo-ship-suez-canal-trapped/507-3ca6964c-3ac2-4b13-867c-38d87366ea5d|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自通航始自亞洲向歐洲與北非的多數航運都途徑蘇伊士運河，使其成為絕對關鍵的通道<ref name="rte">{{Cite news|date=2021-03-24|title=What are the consequences of Suez Canal incident?|work=[[愛爾蘭廣播電視|愛爾蘭廣播電視]]|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/world/2021/0324/1205936-suez-canal-maritime-trade/|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325214904/https://www.rte.ie/news/world/2021/0324/1205936-suez-canal-maritime-trade/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|National Maritime College of Ireland|愛爾蘭國家海事學院}}講師及前任船長比爾·卡瓦納（Bill Kavanagh）將在蘇伊士運河航行的經歷描述為「一項非常複雜且高風險的作業」；在运河上，一陣陣吹向貨櫃的风会把他们变得「像船帆一樣」，使像長賜輪這樣沉重的船隻获得大量[[動量|動量]]，出现難以控制的飘动<ref>{{Cite news|last=Fox|first=Jackie|date=2021-03-25|title=Irish expert describes 'high-risk' transit of Suez Canal|work=[[愛爾蘭廣播電視|RTÉ]]|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/world/2021/0325/1206144-suez-canal-expert/|access-date=2021-03-25|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326031203/https://www.rte.ie/news/world/2021/0325/1206144-suez-canal-expert/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在事件發生之前的幾年中，蘇伊士運河上有許多船隻擱淺。2016年2月25日，[[散貨船|散貨船]]New Katerina号從[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]前往[[青岛市|青岛市]]時在運河上擱淺，十二天后New Katerina号重新上水，在此期間運河航运沒有受到影響<ref>{{Cite web|title=Grounded Bulker Refloated in Suez Canal|url=https://www.maritime-executive.com/article/grounded-bulker-new-katerina-refloated-in-suez-canal|access-date=2021-03-25|website=The Maritime Executive|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308115811/http://www.maritime-executive.com/article/grounded-bulker-new-katerina-refloated-in-suez-canal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年4月28日，[[貨櫃船|貨櫃船]]{{tsl|en|MSC Fabiola|MSC Fabiola}}号遇到發動機問題後在[[大苦湖|大苦湖]]上擱淺，迫使運河官員暫時停止運河中的所有北行和南行交通，MSC Fabiola号於30日脫淺，並繼續穿過運河<ref>{{Cite web|title=Grounded Container Ship Blocks Suez Canal|url=https://www.maritime-executive.com/article/container-ship-grounding-blocks-suez-canal|access-date=2021-03-25|website=The Maritime Executive|language=en|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708054418/http://maritime-executive.com/article/container-ship-grounding-blocks-suez-canal|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Grounded Container Ship in Suez Canal Refloated|url=https://www.maritime-executive.com/article/grounded-container-ship-in-suez-canal-refloated|access-date=2021-03-25|website=The Maritime Executive|language=en|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504103039/http://www.maritime-executive.com/article/grounded-container-ship-in-suez-canal-refloated|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年7月17日，貨櫃船Aeneas号在運河上擱淺，導致其後的三個散貨船Sakizaya Kalon号，Panamax Alexander号和Osios David号相撞<ref>{{Cite web|title=Multiple ship groundings and collisions lead to Suez Canal chaos|url=https://www.ship-technology.com/news/suez-canal-grinds-to-a-halt-after-multi-ship-groundings-collisions/|access-date=2021-03-25|website=www.ship-technology.com|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020143302/https://www.ship-technology.com/news/suez-canal-grinds-to-a-halt-after-multi-ship-groundings-collisions/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Multi-Vessel Pileup in Suez Canal|url=https://www.maritime-executive.com/article/multi-vessel-pileup-in-suez-canal|access-date=2021-03-25|website=The Maritime Executive|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804035809/https://maritime-executive.com/article/multi-vessel-pileup-in-suez-canal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這些事件大多數對蘇伊士運河的交通影響相對較小。

通常當一艘船通過運河時，將會由[[引水人|登船的埃及運河當局領航員]]駕駛，而不是由最初的船員駕駛<ref name=":4" />。

長賜輪是一艘[[長榮黃金級貨櫃船|長榮黃金級貨櫃船]]，是[[最大貨櫃船列表|世界上最大的貨櫃船之一]]，船长399.98米，宽58.8米<ref>{{cite web |title=M.V. EVER GIVEN スエズ運河座礁事故に関して |url=http://www.shoei-kisen.com/shared/210325.html |website=正栄汽船株式会社 |date=2021-03-25 |language=ja |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326183352/http://www.shoei-kisen.com/shared/210325.html |archivedate=2021-03-26 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2021-03-26 }}</ref>。它於2015年12月25日{{tsl|en|Keel laying|鋪設龍骨}}，於2018年5月9日下水，並於2018年9月25日完成<ref>{{Cite web|title=ABS: American Bureau of Shipping|url=https://www.eagle.org/portal/#/absrecord/extSearch?Classno=18265351&Accesstype=PUBLIC&ReferrerApplication=PUBLIC|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301094231/https://www.eagle.org/portal/#/absrecord/extSearch?Classno=18265351&Accesstype=PUBLIC&ReferrerApplication=PUBLIC|archive-date=2021-03-01|access-date=2021-03-25|website=www.eagle.org|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它由[[今治造船|今治造船]]的子公司[[正榮汽船|正榮汽船]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103250280.aspx |title=日本正榮汽船為長榮長賜輪擱淺致歉 直言脫淺極為困難 |author=黃名璽 |date=2021-03-25 |publisher=中央通訊社 |accessdate=2021-03-27 |location=東京 |language=zh-hant |editor=陳政一 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328134532/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103250280.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>擁有，並由[[長榮海運|長榮海運]]以論時傭船（Time Charter）方式承租<ref>{{Cite web |title=擱淺蘇伊士長榮貨輪為「論時傭船」 船員由船東公司派遣 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103240327.aspx |accessdate=2021-03-28 |author=蔡芃敏 |date=2021-03-24 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |location=台北 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328135003/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103240327.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，只運長榮的貨<ref>{{Cite web|title=長榮貨輪卡運河「會被多國求償？」 內行指1關鍵：反而可以開口討|url=https://finance.ettoday.net/news/1945924|author=曾筠淇|date=2021-03-25|accessdate=2021-03-28|publisher=ETtoday新聞雲|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331204235/https://finance.ettoday.net/news/1945924|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該船在[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]]{{tsl|en|Ship registration|船舶註冊|註冊}}<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|date=2021-03-24|title=Giant ship blocking Suez canal partially refloated|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/mar/24/huge-container-ship-blocks-suez-canal-evergreen|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325021309/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/mar/24/huge-container-ship-blocks-suez-canal-evergreen|archive-date=2021-03-25|access-date=2021-03-25|website=the Guardian|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

长赐号原定计划航线由[[深圳|深圳]][[盐田港|盐田港]]出发，经停[[台北|台北]]和[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]，并于3月31日在[[荷兰|荷兰]][[鹿特丹港|鹿特丹港]]靠岸<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.pts.org.tw/article/518811 |title=長賜號卡蘇伊士運河衝擊全球海運 每小時損失上看114億台幣 |date=2021-03-25 |work=公視新聞網 |author2=陳信隆 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326205314/https://news.pts.org.tw/article/518811 |archivedate=2021-03-26 |dead-url=no |author1=黃立偉 |accessdate=2021-03-26 }}</ref>。

== 事件 ==
事發時長賜輪正從馬來西亞[[丹绒柏勒巴斯港|丹绒柏勒巴斯港]]前往荷蘭[[鹿特丹港|鹿特丹港]]，船上載有20,000個貨櫃的貨物<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|date=2021-03-24|title=Egypt's Suez Canal blocked by huge container ship|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-56505413|access-date=2021-03-25|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323234228/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-56505413|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-03-25|title=Suez Canal Blocked a Second Full Day|work=Voice of America|url=https://www.voanews.com/middle-east/suez-canal-blocked-second-full-day|access-date=2021-03-25|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325214929/https://www.voanews.com/middle-east/suez-canal-blocked-second-full-day|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當它擱淺時，它在北行船隊中排序第五，後面有十五艘船<ref name="upi" />。

在2021年3月23日07:40，長賜輪正穿過蘇伊士運河時被沙塵暴困住，船隻被高達{{convert|40|kn|km/h|order=flip}}的強風吹襲，導致船體失控偏離航道<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name="bloomberg">{{Cite web|last1=Wang|first1=Cindy|last2=Park|first2=Kyunghee|last3=Lee|first3=Annie|date=2021-03-23|title=Suez Canal Snarled With Giant Ship Stuck in Top Trade Artery|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-23/suez-canal-traffic-blocked-by-container-ship-stuck-in-waterway|publisher=[[彭博新聞社|Bloomberg News]]|access-date=2021-03-24|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324042433/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-23/suez-canal-traffic-blocked-by-container-ship-stuck-in-waterway|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然後長賜輪在{{cvt|151|km|nmi}}處打橫擱淺，阻塞了兩側的運河<ref name=":0" />。苏伊士运河管理局两名官员指是长赐号船长错误操作導致船隻偏航<ref>{{cite news |title=苏伊士运河管理局官员：“长赐”号船长错误操作致船首严重偏航 |url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_12020868 |accessdate=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2021-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802141258/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_12020868 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

長賜輪阻塞了運河兩邊的200多艘船，其中包括五艘其他類似大小的貨櫃船<ref name="lloydslist">{{cite web |url=https://lloydslist.maritimeintelligence.informa.com/LL1136246/Suez-blockage-extends-as-salvors-fail-to-free-Ever-Given |title=Suez blockage extends as salvors fail to free Ever Given |last=Meade |first=Richard |date=2021-03-25 |publisher=Lloyd's List |access-date=2021-03-25 |quote=Rough calculations suggest westbound traffic is worth around $5.1bn daily while eastbound traffic is worth $4.5bn. |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325215810/https://lloydslist.maritimeintelligence.informa.com/LL1136246/Suez-blockage-extends-as-salvors-fail-to-free-Ever-Given |dead-url=no }}</ref>、41艘[[散貨船|散貨船]]、24艘[[油輪|油輪]]<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-03-26|title=Suez blockage is holding up $9.6bn of goods a day|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/business-56533250|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326024224/https://www.bbc.com/news/business-56533250|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[俄羅斯海軍|俄羅斯海軍]][[阿勒泰級補給艦|阿勒泰級補給艦]]Kola号，後者在同日早些時候曾與另一艘船發生輕微碰撞<ref name="kola.fleetmon">{{Cite web|date=2021-03-24|title=Bulk carrier collided with Russian Navy tanker off Suez {{!}} KOLA – Flee…|url=http://archive.is/Uhgai|access-date=2021-03-25|website=archive.is|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507034750/http://archive.is/Uhgai|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="kola.marinetraffic">{{Cite web|date=2021-03-25|title=KOLA (Oil Products Tanker) Registered in Russia – Vessel details, Cur…|url=http://archive.is/ip8yy|access-date=2021-03-25|website=archive.is|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507034703/http://archive.is/ip8yy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="kola.vesselfinder">{{Cite web|date=2021-03-25|title=KOLA, Oil Products Tanker – Details and current position – IMO 672000…|url=http://archive.is/mTvFG|access-date=2021-03-25|website=archive.is|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507034608/http://archive.is/mTvFG|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受影響的船隻合共約有1690萬[[公噸|噸]]的[[載重噸位|載重量]]{{r|lloydslist}}。部分船隻停靠在該地區的港口，許多則留在原地。也有一些船只放弃该路线，转而选择繞行[[非洲|非洲]][[好望角|好望角]]航道<ref name=":2" />。

工作人員們將長賜輪後的兩艘船移開，以便為[[打撈|打撈]]作業騰出空間，並將長賜輪上的燃料，[[壓艙水|壓艙水]]和幾個貨櫃從船上卸下，以減輕重量好讓重型機械挖出船身<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Paris|first1=Costas|last2=Faucon|first2=Benoit|date=2021-03-25|title=Suez Canal Backlog Grows as Efforts Resume to Free Trapped Ship|work=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/suez-canal-backlog-grows-as-efforts-resume-to-free-trapped-tanker-11616668644|access-date=2021-03-25|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325215239/https://www.wsj.com/articles/suez-canal-backlog-grows-as-efforts-resume-to-free-trapped-tanker-11616668644|dead-url=no}}</ref>。八艘[[拖船|拖船]]嘗試將長賜輪拉離岸邊<ref>{{Cite web |title=Suez Canal suspends traffic as tug boats work to free ship: Live |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/economy/2021/3/25/suez-canal-still-blocked-causing-massive-shipping-jam-live |language=en |access-date=2021-03-25 |website=Aljazeera |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325102338/https://www.aljazeera.com/economy/2021/3/25/suez-canal-still-blocked-causing-massive-shipping-jam-live |dead-url=no }}</ref>。挖泥船和[[挖掘機|挖掘機]]也被用來挖出貨船前端周圍的沙土<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202103260187.aspx |title=長榮貨輪擱淺蘇伊士運河 挖沙2萬立方公尺才有救 |author=曾依璇 |date=2021-03-25 |publisher=中央通訊社 |accessdate=2021-03-27 |location=開羅 |language=zh-hant |editor=張正芊 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328134239/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202103260187.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2021/03/25/middleeast/suez-canal-ship-blockage-intl-hnk/index.html |title=Dislodging the huge ship blocking the Suez Canal could take 'days to weeks,' as the traffic jam builds |website=CNN |date=2021-03-25 |access-date=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325122427/https://edition.cnn.com/2021/03/25/middleeast/suez-canal-ship-blockage-intl-hnk/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。船隻救援公司[[Boskalis|Boskalis]]的行政總裁彼得·贝尔多夫斯基（Peter Berdowski）表示，該作業「可能需要幾天到幾週的時間」<ref>{{Cite web|last=Hebron|first=Herbert F.|date=2021-03-25|title=Refloating the Suez Canal can take weeks: 'Very heavy whale on the beach' {{!}} NOW {{!}} EN24 News|url=https://www.en24news.com/now/2021/03/refloating-the-suez-canal-can-take-weeks-very-heavy-whale-on-the-beach-now.html|access-date=2021-03-25|website=en24news|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326031205/https://www.en24news.com/now/2021/03/refloating-the-suez-canal-can-take-weeks-very-heavy-whale-on-the-beach-now.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

3月25日，[[蘇伊士運河管理局|蘇伊士運河管理局]]暫停船隻通過蘇伊士運河，要到長賜輪重新航行後，才恢復其他船隻通過<ref>{{Cite web|title=Suez Canal suspends traffic as tug boats work to free ship: Live|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/economy/2021/3/25/suez-canal-still-blocked-causing-massive-shipping-jam-live|access-date=2021-03-25|website=www.aljazeera.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325102338/https://www.aljazeera.com/economy/2021/3/25/suez-canal-still-blocked-causing-massive-shipping-jam-live|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-25|title=Suez Canal suspends traffic in bid to refloat ship|url=https://www.rte.ie/news/world/2021/0325/1205987-suez-canal/|language=en|publisher=[[愛爾蘭廣播電視|愛爾蘭廣播電視]]|access-date=2021-03-25|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326031206/https://www.rte.ie/news/world/2021/0325/1205987-suez-canal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根據長榮海運3月25日發布之說明稿表示，長賜輪船員、船舶、貨物皆安全無虞，無海洋污染情形，同時澄清該輪擱淺前並無外傳跳電的狀況發生。此外，長賜輪為租船，故其脫困及衍生之第三人責任等相關費用以及船體等損失係由船東負責。<ref>{{cite web |author1=長榮海運 |title=M/V Ever Given 長賜輪在蘇伊士運河擱淺事件之說明 - 0325 |url=https://www.evergreen-marine.com/news/202103/CMS_NEWS2021032600007942_20210326011103_A63A11D2D663408AAD9C3928D28EDFDC.pdf |accessdate=2021-03-26 |archive-date=2021-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331204222/https://www.evergreen-marine.com/news/202103/CMS_NEWS2021032600007942_20210326011103_A63A11D2D663408AAD9C3928D28EDFDC.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{link-en|土耳其运输部|Ministry_of_Transport_and_Infrastructure_(Turkey)}}部长{{link-en|阿迪尔·卡拉伊斯梅洛卢|Adil Karaismailoğlu}}同日宣布准备为搁浅货轮提供援助<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|title=Video: UPDATE - Suez Canal Authority says 321 ships left waiting to cross the Suez Canal due to blockage|url=https://egyptindependent.com/video-update-suez-canal-authority-says-321-ships-left-waiting-to-cross-the-suez-canal-due-to-blockage/|accessdate=2021-03-27|date=2021-03-27|work=Egypt Independent|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328011922/https://www.egyptindependent.com/video-update-suez-canal-authority-says-321-ships-left-waiting-to-cross-the-suez-canal-due-to-blockage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

3月26日，埃及苏伊士运河管理局宣布清除長賜輪周围沉积物的工程已经完成，但还须要满足风向和[[潮汐|潮汐]]等条件才可移-{}-动船只，而随着船舶的规模和重量也引起了打捞行业的担忧。负责打捞行业的荷兰[[Boskalis|Boskalis]]行政總裁彼得·贝尔多夫斯基指，在苏伊士运河这样的密闭空间中移动一艘巨型船只将是一项艰巨的挑战。对于未来的工作，相关人员认为「最好的方案是在涨潮时用拖船拉離，但是如果不可能的话，减轻船只的重量是唯一的选择，但这也导致将花费更长的时间」<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=スエズ運河 コンテナ船座礁 周辺の土砂取り除く作業終わる|url=https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20210327/k10012940091000.html|accessdate=2021-03-27|last=日本放送協会|work=NHKニュース|archive-date=2021-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328124142/https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20210327/k10012940091000.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，長賜輪的船舵和螺旋桨恢复运行，但无法预测何时脱浅<ref name=":6" />。苏伊士运河管理局负责人乌萨马·拉比（Osama Rabie）表示，自河道阻塞了航行后，约有321艘船等待穿越水道，也表示希望没有必要从船上卸下集装箱来减轻船重负担的工程，但因为强劲的海浪和大风使的当局的努力变得更加复杂<ref name=":6">{{Cite news|title=Ship stranded in Suez Canal has moved but unclear when it will be freed- SCA Chairman|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/business/ship-stranded-in-suez-canal-has-moved-but-unclear-when-it-will-be-freed-sca-chairman/articleshow/81726357.cms?from=mdr|newspaper=The Economic Times|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2021-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331204235/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/business/ship-stranded-in-suez-canal-has-moved-but-unclear-when-it-will-be-freed-sca-chairman/articleshow/81726357.cms?from=mdr|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亦表示强风和沙尘暴并不是导致货轮搁浅事故的主要原因，认为重大事故往往是「综合」原因<ref name=":5" />。

3月28日，货轮管理方表示，长赐轮的船头受损，河水涌入了两个船舱。他们使用了大功率泵将水从船舱中抽出来，船体状态稳定<ref>{{cite news |title=“长赐”号货轮船头出现破损，目前状态稳定 |url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/5874900.html |work=界面新闻 |date=2021-03-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329055748/https://www.jiemian.com/article/5874900.html |archivedate=2021-03-29 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2021-03-29 }}</ref>。

3月29日，長賜輪重新浮起，並在拖船的協助下駛離原擱淺的河道，在检查运河受损情况后，运河管理局宣佈其于当地时间19:00恢復雙向交通<ref>{{Cite web |title=長榮長賜輪擱淺第7天脫困 蘇伊士運河交通將恢復 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103295005.aspx |accessdate=2021-03-29 |author=蔡芃敏 |date=2021-03-29 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |editor=潘羿菁 |location=台北 |archive-date=2021-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331204224/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103295005.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Debre">{{Cite web |title=Giant container ship that blocked Suez Canal finally free |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/container-ship-stuck-in-suez-canal-partially-refloated/2021/03/29/2923462e-9044-11eb-aadc-af78701a30ca_story.html |accessdate=2021-03-29 |publisher=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |language=en-US |author1=Isabel Debre |author2=Samy Magdy |issn=0190-8286 |archive-date=2021-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329225723/https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/container-ship-stuck-in-suez-canal-partially-refloated/2021/03/29/2923462e-9044-11eb-aadc-af78701a30ca_story.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Al Jazeera traffic resumes">{{cite web | title=Traffic in Suez Canal resumes after stranded ship refloated - Business and Economy News | website=Al Jazeera | date=2021-03-29 | url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/3/29/traffic-in-suez-canal-resumes-after-stranded-ship-refloated | access-date=2021-03-29 | quote=The ship came out intact and it has no problems. We’ve just searched the bottom and soil of the Suez Canal and thankfully it is sound and has no issues, and ships will pass through it today | archive-date=2021-03-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329225718/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/3/29/traffic-in-suez-canal-resumes-after-stranded-ship-refloated | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而後该船曾因大风而再次短暂封锁运河<ref name="Pippa Stevens"/><ref>{{Cite web |title=“长赐号”再次被移动 苏伊士运河交通恢复 |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/42VU8NVlD8a |accessdate=2021-03-30 |author=乌元春 |date=2021-03-29 |publisher=環球時報 |language=zh-hans |editor=楊陽 |archive-date=2021-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331204226/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/42VU8NVlD8a |dead-url=no }}</ref>，長賜輪亦前往運河中段「[[大苦湖|大苦湖]]」接受調查。

4月13日，埃及一家法院判決长赐号必須支付完9亿美元赔偿金才能離開蘇伊士運河<ref>{{cite news |title=赔偿9亿美元才能离开！“长赐号”货轮遭埃及扣押 |url=https://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/04-14/9454278.shtml |accessdate=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415013342/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/04-14/9454278.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。长赐轮的承保公司对赔偿价格不认可，并对扣押船只表示失望<ref>{{cite web |title=“Ever Given” re-floated in Suez Canal |url=https://www.ukpandi.com/news-and-resources/press-release-articles/2021/ever-given-grounding-in-suez-canal/ |work=UK P&I |language=en |date=2021-04-13 |accessdate=2021-04-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413222719/https://www.ukpandi.com/news-and-resources/press-release-articles/2021/ever-given-grounding-in-suez-canal/ |archivedate=2021-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=不赔9亿美元不能走，埃及扣押“长赐”号货轮，日本船东拒绝付钱，曾还价打一折 |url=http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2021-04-14/1696761.html |work=每经网 |date=2021-04-14 |accessdate=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416095826/http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2021-04-14/1696761.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

5月12日，苏伊士运河管理局提交的苏伊士运河南段航道拓宽计划得到埃及當局批准，拓寬計劃將在两年内完成<ref>{{cite news |title=经历过堵塞事件后苏伊士运河要拓宽：计划两年内完成 |url=https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1126685.htm |accessdate=2021-05-12 |archive-date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513143548/https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1126685.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

6月23日，蘇伊士運河管理局表示雙方已經達成和解，賠償金額並未公開，由船東、貨主及航商共同分擔。<ref>{{cite web |title=長賜輪「贖金」終於談好！SCA：令人滿意將放行 |url=https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3580518 |accessdate=2022-05-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=長賜輪擱淺賠償結果出爐 日船東將與貨主、航商協調分攤5億5000萬美元 |url=https://news.pts.org.tw/article/533870 |accessdate=2022-05-15}}</ref>

