== 經濟影響 ==
[[File:Suez_Canal_traffic_jam_seen_from_space.jpg|thumb]]衛星於運河堵塞前（左，3月21日）與堵塞期間（右，3月25日）所拍攝的衛星照顯示，運河的交通阻塞造成[[蘇伊士灣|蘇伊士灣]]聚集了大量船隻]]
蘇伊士運河掌管了全球約12%的貿易流量，每天約有五十艘船通過運河<ref name=":4" />。專家警告，此事件可能會導致全球消費者的日常物品運輸延遲<ref>{{Cite web|title='Anything you see in the stores' could be affected by Canal logjam, shipping experts say|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/business/economy/massive-container-ship-blocking-suez-could-delay-shipments-raise-gas-n1261950|last=Popken|first=Ben|date=2021-03-25|access-date=2021-03-25|website=NBC News|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325045425/https://www.nbcnews.com/business/economy/massive-container-ship-blocking-suez-could-delay-shipments-raise-gas-n1261950|dead-url=no}}</ref>。海事歷史學家薩爾·梅爾科利亞諾（Sal Mercogliano）說：「運河一關閉……貨櫃船和油輪就不能向歐洲運送食品，燃料和製成品，也不能從歐洲向遠東出口貨物。」<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":4" />  

[[勞埃德船舶日報|勞埃德船舶日報]]估計，清除障礙物所需的每一天將打亂價值90億[[美元|美元]]商品的運輸<ref name="lloydslist"></ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-25|title=Shipping losses mount from cargo vessel stuck in Suez Canal|url=https://apnews.com/article/cargo-ship-stuck-suez-canal-egypt-d8b6696716ab45794cba583ecf0e4001|access-date=2021-03-25|website=AP NEWS|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325201657/https://apnews.com/article/cargo-ship-stuck-suez-canal-egypt-d8b6696716ab45794cba583ecf0e4001|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有顧問指出，蘇伊士運河即使是短期中斷，也會誘發整個供應鏈中持續幾個月的骨牌效應<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/suez-canal-egypt-ever-given-1.5963207|title=Ship stuck in Suez Canal disrupting nearly $10B of goods every day as 150-boat backlog grows|publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|author=[[美联社|The Associated Press]]|date=2021-03-25|access-date=2021-03-25|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326031212/https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/suez-canal-egypt-ever-given-1.5963207|dead-url=no}}</ref>，運輸成本將上漲<ref>{{cite news |title=蘇伊士運河：從數字看「長賜號」擱淺的影響 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56561264.amp |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2021-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331204247/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56561264.amp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。航道堵塞期間[[蘇伊士運河管理局|蘇伊士運河管理局]]每天的運河營運收入減少約1400萬至1500萬美元<ref>{{cite news |title=「長賜號」脫困 蘇伊士運河堵塞的經濟損失和關鍵看點 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56563579 |accessdate=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2021-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330141537/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56563579 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[彭博新聞社|彭博]]指如果蘇伊士運河的阻塞情況持續，依賴此航道取得中東石油的欧美煉油廠可能被迫要找替代來源。如此一來有可能推高地區油價<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2021-03-25/suez-canal-blocked-what-a-lengthy-closure-will-mean-for-the-oil-price |title=Faltering demand isn’t the only reason crude markets have been unmoved by the Suez blockage. The waterway just isn’t what it once was for oil tankers. |publisher=彭博 |accessdate=2021-03-26 |archive-date=2021-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329113536/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2021-03-25/suez-canal-blocked-what-a-lengthy-closure-will-mean-for-the-oil-price |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[亞洲|亞洲]]和[[歐洲|歐洲]]之間海上運輸的替代路線是繞行[[非洲|非洲]]的[[好望角|好望角]]航線，航程增加約{{cvt|6480|km|nmi}}，耗時增加約9至10天<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2021-03-26/suez-blockage-should-not-drive-up-petrol-prices/100030246 |title=Ever Given Suez Canal blockage should not drive up petrol prices, but Easter might |first=Michael |last=Janda |website=[[澳大利亚广播公司|ABC]] |date=2021-03-26 |access-date=2021-03-26 |archive-date=2021-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326235936/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2021-03-26/suez-blockage-should-not-drive-up-petrol-prices/100030246 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=If Lin |author2=Steven Yeo |author3=游承穎 |title=讓蘇伊士運河「大排長榮」的長賜輪到底有多大？我們把它放到台北市看看 |url=https://www.thenewslens.com/article/148911 |work=關鍵評論網 |publisher=TNL Media Group |date=2021-03-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327121342/https://www.thenewslens.com/article/148911 |archivedate=2021-03-27 |language=zh-tw |accessdate=2021-03-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。也有企業嘗試[[中歐班列|中歐班列]]，但運費要上漲30%至40%<ref>{{cite news |title=苏伊士运河拥堵让“可供运力减半”，替代方案有哪些？ |url=https://www.yicai.com/news/100999053.html |accessdate=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325082204/https://www.yicai.com/news/100999053.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

